                        <interp inst="t18771022-751-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. <hi rend="italic">He was further charged with a conviction of a similar offence in January</hi>, 1875, <hi rend="italic">at Maidstone, in the name of <persName id="t18771022-name-31">
                        <interp inst="t18771022-name-31" type="gender" value="indeterminate"></interp>
